title.rendered: BOSS AIR 12V COMPRESSOR TANK AIRBAG INFLATION COMBO

content.rendered:
BOSS AIR 12V COMPRESSOR TANK AIRBAG INFLATION COMBO

Boss Air 12V Compressor Tank Airbag Inflation Combo available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

12v Compressor Tank and simple inflation package for your all-in-one air source solution with no additional plumbing required. Compressor is mounted into the air tank ready to go.

Includes auto cutout at 140psi with a 100-140psi pressure switch.

This combo includes:

  • Tank 1gallon
  • Pressure Gauge
  • 110-140psi pressure switch
  • Drain tap
  • Complete simple inflation kit with 10mtrs of quality Boss 1/4″ Airline
  • Inbuilt Compressor
  • 12v DC
  • 25% duty cycle@100psi
  • 1.9cfm
  • Max amp draw 20amps
  • Max working pressure 150psi

Extra options available include:

  • Gauge Kit
    • Dual needle gauge 200psi with fittings and 10mtrs of Airline
  • 1/4″ Airline Fittings Kit
    • 1/4″ Airline valve fitting kit sealant-less
  • Remote Nitto Add-on
    • Add a remote Nitto Coupling so you can “plug-in” to pump up tyres or use air tools
To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
